for studying\nstrongly-correlated systems, as: (i) it works in the thermodynamic limit, (ii)\nis comparable in accuracy to VMC, and (iii) has numerical complexity comparable\nto GA (i.e., it provides the results much faster than the VMC approach).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jan 2014 10:19:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-22"}
